data.description: Introducing a stunning new listing in Fayetteville, Georgia! This move-in ready property offers the perfect combination of luxury, functionality, and convenience. With five bedrooms, four full bathrooms, and a generous 3,162 square feet of living space, there is ample room for the whole family to thrive. Situated on a spacious 1.05-acre lot, this home boasts a timeless elegance with its stunning four-sided brick exterior. Step inside and be greeted by an open floor concept that flows seamlessly from the formal dining area with 9-foot arches and elegant molding to the formal living room. The 15-foot family room with coffered ceilings leads to the kitchen, which is surrounded by 42-inch cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of counter space. Imagine preparing delicious meals while enjoying the warmth of the fireplace, setting the perfect mood after a long day. One standout feature of this home is the inclusion of a bedroom and full bath on the main level, making it ideal for accommodating an older child or parent who prefers single-level living. The stairs in the middle of the house lead you to the master bedroom, a true sanctuary with its oversized layout and a step-up sitting room with 15-foot ceilings. Two of the bedrooms are conjoined with a Jack and Jill bathroom, while the fourth bedroom has its own bathroom. Each room offers ample closet space and natural light, creating a welcoming atmosphere. The backyard is spacious and flat, perfect for creating your own outdoor oasis. Beyond the confines of this remarkable property, the community itself is a haven for outdoor enthusiasts. With two nearby parks at your disposal, you'll have ample opportunities to enjoy the beauty of nature. The parks feature fields for soccer and football, as well as playgrounds for children to explore and have fun. Another advantage of this location is its proximity to the renowned trailer studios, which are less than 3 miles away. Whether you're a fan of the film industry or simply appreciate the allure of movie sets, living close to a renowned studio adds an exciting element to your lifestyle. Don't miss out on the chance to make this exquisite Fayetteville listing your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the perfect combination of luxury, functionality, and convenience in this move-in ready property.
